 the simple model of energy\npropagation versus height, although a more detailed model for the flaring solar\natmosphere is needed. And finally, we detected marginal quasi-periodic\npulsations (QPPs) in the 40--60 second range for the Ca~K, Mg and H$\\alpha$\nbands, and such measurements are important for disentangling the detailed\nflare-physics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 Nov 2018 02:07:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Feb 2019 19:06:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-24"}
