ion on the\ncell membrane and one-dimensional cytoplasm-membrane adsorption. With the\nmodel, we examine the contribution of the 2D reaction pathway to the overall\nreaction rate at different reactant diffusivity, reactivity and concentrations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 Nov 2018 07:52:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-24"}
